name: side-scan-sonar-lines-for-hudson-river-ny
notes: Side Scan Sonar and Subbottom Profiler Tracklines. Data was collected November 5 to December 15, 2009, in the estuary north from Saugerties to Troy. Fugro utilized the GeoAcoustics GeoSwath and the EdgeTech SB216 Chirp subbottom profiler system for data collection. Tracklines were created with CARIS 7.0
